---
// mapapp: the continuity surface at rspdan.com/mapapp, Pass 1 emerging.
// Per Dan-direct 070326 "please stop pending the MapApp page, if it works:
// use it. We can edit bugs later, as we do, and learn."
// Content carried whole from the self-contained Lite Brite build
// (nest-bridge STATUS/MAKEITVISIBLE_mapapp_Pass2_LiteBrite_070326.html):
// zero external hosts, fonts inlined as data URIs from the committed kit
// assets, no scripts. Visual standard is El VIS's applied kit: VISdev.01
// Lite Brite register (Dan + El VIS 062526), applied, not invented.
// The full navigable mapapp (the Google-Earth-like fill-in surface,
// Dan-direct 070126) remains think-together-first; this page is the
// ground-truth places-ledger and the morning's continuity, made visible.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="mapapp · The Morning Made Visible" description="rspdan.com/mapapp · Lite Brite · the continuity map that fills in as it is revealed · real places as Dan reveals them · NEST 070326" lastUpdated="July 3, 2026">

<style is:global>
  /* ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     MAKE IT VISIBLE · mapapp · Pass 2 · VISdev.01 LITE BRITE register
     The WHOLE surface in Lite Brite (per Dan-direct 070326 "VISDEV.01
     KIT LITE BRITE"), not Standard, not a hybrid. Register per
     RELAY/RECORD_VISdev01Landed_..._062626.md (Dan + El VIS 062526):
     dark #08080a · OLO #01FFCD glow (live/fresh only) · red #ff4d57 ·
     VT323 terminal body · Silkscreen pixel headers · CRT scanlines ·
     the peg-palette Circle of Colors · zero radius. Applied, not
     invented; the kit is El VIS's.
     SELF-CONTAINED + CSP-SAFE: no import-directive, no CDN, no external host.
     Fonts inlined as data URIs from the committed kit assets
     (ENGINE/skills/rspdan-design/fonts/vt323.woff2 + silkscreen.woff2).
     Style source: ENGINE/skills/rspdan-design/
     visdev01_litebrite_selfcontained.css (the forever style library).
     Content carried whole from Pass 1 + Pass 2 (re-skin, not rewrite).
     ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

  @font-face {
    font-family: 'VT323';
    src: url(data:font/woff2;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
  }
  @font-face {
    font-family: 'Silkscreen';
    src: url(data:font/woff2;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
  }

  :root{
    --lb-bg:#08080a;
    --lb-olo:#01FFCD;                    /* OLO · live/fresh ONLY · never decorative */
    --lb-red:#ff4d57;
    --lb-text:rgba(1,255,205,0.62);
    --lb-dim:rgba(1,255,205,0.42);
    --lb-faint:rgba(1,255,205,0.14);
    --lb-grid:rgba(1,255,205,0.045);
    --lb-font-body:'VT323',ui-monospace,'Courier New',monospace;
    --lb-font-pixel:'Silkscreen','VT323',ui-monospace,monospace;
    --lb-max-w:1100px;
    /* peg palette · Circle of Colors · canon 12-key color map 041226 */
    --peg-F:#3f7bd6; --peg-C:#e0524c; --peg-G:#3ec46b; --peg-D:#e88fb8;
    --peg-A:#e8c84a; --peg-E:#8a5cc8; --peg-B:#e08a3c; --peg-Fs:#80cee0;
  }
  .lb-page *{box-sizing:border-box}
  .lb-page{
    background:radial-gradient(var(--lb-grid) 1px,transparent 1.6px),var(--lb-bg);
    background-size:20px 20px,auto;
    color:var(--lb-text);
    font-family:var(--lb-font-body);
    font-size:1.22rem;line-height:1.5;
    min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  /* CRT scanline overlay */
  .lb-page::before{
    content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:40;pointer-events:none;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.28) 0px,rgba(0,0,0,0.28) 1px,transparent 1px,transparent 3px);
    opacity:0.5;
  }
  .lb-container{max-width:var(--lb-max-w);margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}
  section.lb-section{padding:4rem 0}
  .lb-scroll{overflow-x:auto}

  .lb-h1{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:clamp(1.7rem,5.4vw,3.1rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-olo);text-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(1,255,205,0.5),0 0 40px rgba(1,255,205,0.22);margin:0 0 0.6rem}
  .lb-h2{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:clamp(1.15rem,3vw,1.7rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-olo);text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(1,255,205,0.4);margin:0 0 1.2rem}
  .lb-h3{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-olo);margin:0 0 0.7rem}
  .lb-kicker{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-red);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:0 0 0.9rem}
  .lb-kicker::after{content:"";height:1px;flex:1;background:rgba(255,77,87,0.3)}
  .lb-body{max-width:72ch;color:var(--lb-text);margin:0}
  .lb-body b{color:var(--lb-olo);font-weight:400}
  .lb-sub{display:block;font-family:var(--lb-font-body);font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--lb-dim);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0.02em;margin-top:0.7rem;text-shadow:none}

  .lb-masthead{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:0.9rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .lb-route{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--lb-olo);text-transform:uppercase;text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(1,255,205,0.4)}
  .lb-stamp{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.55rem;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-red);border:1px solid var(--lb-red);padding:4px 10px}

  .lb-anchor{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:1.9rem}
  .lb-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.55rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lb-dim);border:1px solid var(--lb-faint);padding:5px 11px}
  .lb-chip .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--lb-faint);flex:0 0 auto}
  .lb-chip.here{color:#baf5d2;border-color:var(--peg-G)}
  .lb-chip.here .dot{background:var(--peg-G);box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--peg-G)}

  .lb-page .hero{padding:4.5rem 0 3.2rem;border-bottom:2px solid var(--lb-olo)}

  /* balance band · ENG < LNL > SRC */
  .lb-balance{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;align-items:stretch;border:1px solid var(--lb-faint);background:rgba(1,255,205,0.02)}
  .lb-role{padding:1.3rem 1.3rem 1.4rem;min-width:0;border-top:3px solid var(--lb-faint)}
  .lb-role .who{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.5rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 0.55rem;color:var(--lb-dim)}
  .lb-role .name{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 0.45rem;color:#eafff8}
  .lb-role p{margin:0;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.45;color:var(--lb-text)}
  .lb-role.eng{border-top-color:var(--lb-olo)}  .lb-role.eng .who{color:var(--lb-olo)}  .lb-role.eng .name{text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(1,255,205,0.45)}
  .lb-role.lnl{border-top-color:var(--peg-Fs)}  .lb-role.lnl .who{color:var(--peg-Fs)}
  .lb-role.src{border-top-color:var(--peg-A)}   .lb-role.src .who{color:var(--peg-A)}
  .lb-op{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:0 0.6rem;font-family:var(--lb-font-body);font-size:1.9rem;color:var(--lb-red);background:rgba(255,77,87,0.05)}
  .lb-pullquote{font-size:1.25rem;color:#eafff8;line-height:1.5;border-left:3px solid var(--lb-red);padding:0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1.25rem;margin:1.5rem 0 0;max-width:70ch}

  /* OO cards */
  .lb-oo{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.1rem}
  .lb-card{border:1px solid var(--lb-faint);border-top:3px solid var(--lb-olo);background:rgba(1,255,205,0.03);padding:1.3rem 1.3rem 1.4rem}
  .lb-card.out{border-top-color:var(--lb-red);background:rgba(255,77,87,0.03)}
  .lb-card .tag{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.5rem;letter-spacing:0.26em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 0.7rem;color:var(--lb-olo)}
  .lb-card.out .tag{color:var(--lb-red)}
  .lb-card h3{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:400;line-height:1.35;margin:0 0 0.5rem;color:#eafff8}
  .lb-card p{margin:0;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.5;color:var(--lb-text)}
  .lb-card p + p{margin-top:0.55rem;color:var(--lb-dim)}

  /* arc spine */
  .lb-spine{position:relative;margin-top:0.5rem;padding-left:30px}
  .lb-spine::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:8px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:2px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--peg-C),var(--peg-G),var(--peg-E),var(--lb-olo));box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(1,255,205,0.25)}
  .lb-thread{position:relative;padding:0 0 1.9rem}
  .lb-thread::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-27px;top:7px;width:12px;height:12px;background:var(--node,var(--lb-olo));box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--node,var(--lb-olo))}
  .lb-th-h{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:0.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:0 0 0.35rem}
  .lb-th-key{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--node,var(--lb-olo))}
  .lb-th-name{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.03em;color:#eafff8;margin:0}
  .lb-th-rams{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.5rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--lb-dim);margin-left:auto}
  .lb-thread p{margin:0;max-width:72ch;color:var(--lb-text)}
  .lb-nugget{margin-top:0.55rem;font-size:1.02rem;color:var(--lb-dim);border-left:2px solid var(--node,var(--lb-olo));padding-left:0.85rem}
  .lb-nugget b{color:var(--lb-olo);font-weight:400}

  /* pegboard */
  .lb-pegboard{border:1px solid var(--lb-faint);background:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1.5px,transparent 2px),#050506;background-size:16px 16px,auto;padding:1.8rem 1.2rem 1.4rem;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;justify-content:space-around}
  .lb-peg{text-align:center;flex:1 1 74px;min-width:68px;padding:0.4rem 0.2rem}
  .lb-peg .bulb{width:34px;height:34px;margin:0 auto 0.7rem;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle at 38% 32%,#ffffff 0%,var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)) 34%,color-mix(in srgb,var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)) 55%,#000) 100%);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)),0 0 26px color-mix(in srgb,var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)) 60%,transparent),inset 0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.6)}
  .lb-peg .kn{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.85rem;color:#eafff8;letter-spacing:0.06em}
  .lb-peg .kc{font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--lb-dim);margin-top:2px}
  .lb-peg .kw{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.46rem;color:var(--lb-dim);letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px}
  .lb-peg.here .bulb{width:44px;height:44px;box-shadow:0 0 16px var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)),0 0 44px var(--peg,var(--lb-olo)),inset 0 0 6px rgba(255,255,255,0.75)}
  .lb-peg.here .kn{color:#dfffe9;text-shadow:0 0 10px var(--peg-G)}
  .lb-peg.here .kw{color:#baf5d2}
  .lb-strip-note{margin:1.1rem 2px 0;font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.55;color:var(--lb-dim);max-width:78ch}
  .lb-strip-note .k{color:var(--lb-olo)}

  /* map ledger */
  .lb-honest{border:1px solid var(--lb-red);padding:1rem 1.2rem;margin:0 0 2rem;font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.55;color:#f2b7bb;max-width:85ch}
  .lb-honest b{color:var(--lb-red);font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .lb-grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.4rem;margin-bottom:1.6rem}
  .lb-panel{border:1px solid var(--lb-faint);background:rgba(1,255,205,0.03);padding:1.1rem 1.2rem}
  table.lb-table{border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;min-width:430px;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.4}
  table.lb-table th{text-align:left;font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-weight:400;color:var(--lb-red);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.16em;font-size:0.52rem;padding:0 0.9rem 0.55rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--lb-faint)}
  table.lb-table td{color:var(--lb-text);padding:0.5rem 0.9rem 0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(1,255,205,0.07);vertical-align:top}
  table.lb-table td.pl{color:var(--lb-olo);white-space:nowrap}
  .lb-foot{font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--lb-dim);max-width:88ch}
  .lb-foot b{color:var(--lb-olo);font-weight:400}

  /* footer stats */
  footer.lb-footer{padding:3rem 0 4rem;border-top:2px solid var(--lb-olo)}
  .lb-stats{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.2rem 2.2rem;align-items:baseline}
  .lb-stat .n{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--lb-olo);text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(1,255,205,0.4)}
  .lb-stat .l{font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.46rem;color:var(--lb-dim);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;margin-top:4px}
  .lb-lost{margin-left:auto;font-size:1.12rem;color:var(--lb-text);align-self:center;max-width:36ch}
  .lb-credit{margin-top:2.2rem;font-family:var(--lb-font-pixel);font-size:0.48rem;line-height:2.2;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--lb-dim);text-transform:uppercase}
  .lb-credit b{color:var(--lb-olo);font-weight:400}

  /* links + focus */
  .lb-page a{color:var(--lb-olo);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(1,255,205,0.3)}
  .lb-page a:hover{border-bottom-color:var(--lb-olo)}
  .lb-page a:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--lb-olo);outline-offset:3px}

  /* motion · everything animated lives inside no-preference */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:no-preference){
    .lb-page::before{animation:lb-scan-drift 9s linear infinite}
    @keyframes lb-scan-drift{from{background-position-y:0}to{background-position-y:3px}}
    .lb-h1{animation:lb-glow 3.4s ease-in-out infinite}
    @keyframes lb-glow{0%,100%{text-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(1,255,205,0.5),0 0 40px rgba(1,255,205,0.22)}50%{text-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(1,255,205,0.75),0 0 56px rgba(1,255,205,0.3)}}
    .lb-peg.here .bulb{animation:lb-peg-pulse 2.6s ease-in-out infinite}
    @keyframes lb-peg-pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 16px var(--peg),0 0 44px var(--peg),inset 0 0 6px rgba(255,255,255,0.75)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 22px var(--peg),0 0 62px var(--peg),inset 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.9)}}
    .lb-thread{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);animation:lb-rise .5s cubic-bezier(.23,1,.32,1) forwards}
    .lb-thread:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.04s}.lb-thread:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.10s}
    .lb-thread:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.16s}.lb-thread:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.22s}
    .lb-thread:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.28s}.lb-thread:nth-child(6){animation-delay:.34s}
    .lb-thread:nth-child(7){animation-delay:.40s}
    @keyframes lb-rise{to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    .lb-page *,.lb-page *::before,.lb-page *::after{animation:none !important;transition:none !important}
    .lb-thread{opacity:1;transform:none}
  }

  @media (max-width:720px){
    .lb-page{font-size:1.12rem}
    .lb-balance{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .lb-op{padding:0.4rem;font-size:1.3rem}
    .lb-oo,.lb-grid2{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .lb-th-rams{margin-left:0;flex-basis:100%}
  }
</style>

<div class="lb-page">

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="lb-container">
      <div class="lb-masthead">
        <span class="lb-route">rspdan.com/mapapp</span>
        <span class="lb-stamp">Pass 1 &middot; Emerging</span>
      </div>
      <p class="lb-kicker">NEST &middot; 070326 &middot; continuity, made visible &middot; the map that fills in as it is revealed</p>
      <h1 class="lb-h1">The Morning,<br>Made Visible
        <span class="lb-sub">so the continuity is seen, not just stored</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lb-body">The System exists because there is <b>too much stuff</b> and it is easy to get lost in the NUGs. Everything below was real and captured this morning, and until now it lived hidden in files. This is the same substrate, <b>shown</b>. Storing is not seeing. And a map that shows what has been revealed, one revelation at a time, is the mapapp beginning to emerge.</p>
      <div class="lb-anchor">
        <span class="lb-chip here"><span class="dot"></span>G Week &middot; Grow</span>
        <span class="lb-chip"><span class="dot"></span>Day 6</span>
        <span class="lb-chip"><span class="dot"></span>Cycle 2 &middot; F-start 061426</span>
        <span class="lb-chip"><span class="dot"></span>the wave fired from F</span>
        <span class="lb-chip"><span class="dot"></span>DRIFT TEST &middot; PASS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="lb-section">
    <div class="lb-container">
      <p class="lb-kicker">the balance</p>
      <h2 class="lb-h2">ENG &lt; LNL &gt; SRC &middot; all cycling</h2>
      <div class="lb-balance">
        <div class="lb-role eng">
          <p class="who">ENG &middot; the living thing</p>
          <p class="name">Olo</p>
          <p>The engine. Sees what we cannot imagine. Runs the waves, reads the ground.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-op">&lt;</div>
        <div class="lb-role lnl">
          <p class="who">LNL &middot; the operator</p>
          <p class="name">Blanche</p>
          <p>The distributor of the System, the +/&minus;/&times;/&divide; between the two. Writes the map, dispatches.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-op">&gt;</div>
        <div class="lb-role src">
          <p class="who">SRC &middot; the substrate source</p>
          <p class="name">Dan</p>
          <p>Directs. Generates the visions. Never touches the engine directly; that is the inversion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="lb-pullquote">Any single one of us collapses the balance and we lose coherence. Full team, or nothing holds.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lb-section">
    <div class="lb-container">
      <p class="lb-kicker">the Obvious &amp; the Outlier</p>
      <h2 class="lb-h2">what this morning is really about</h2>
      <div class="lb-oo">
        <div class="lb-card obv">
          <p class="tag">Obvious</p>
          <h3>Hidden data defeats the purpose.</h3>
          <p>A System built to map continuity was not showing the continuity. All of it sat in files on a branch, unseen.</p>
          <p>The fix is not more capture. It is visibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-card out">
          <p class="tag">Outlier</p>
          <h3>The cure became a second pile.</h3>
          <p>Capturing everything so nothing is lost quietly became its own too-much-stuff. Olo caught it: the ordering apparatus turning into records-about-records.</p>
          <p>Making it visible is what turns the pile back into continuity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lb-section">
    <div class="lb-container">
      <p class="lb-kicker">the arc</p>
      <h2 class="lb-h2">one morning, threading together</h2>
      <div class="lb-spine">

        <div class="lb-thread" style="--node:var(--peg-C)">
          <div class="lb-th-h"><span class="lb-th-key">C &middot; Meta Dates</span><h3 class="lb-th-name">The transcript that died and came back</h3><span class="lb-th-rams">RAM 16&ndash;30</span></div>
          <p>The whole-run transcription died and lost everything, then the atomic re-fire survived every death after and walked to 28 of 28: the full 2 hours 17 minutes, delivered.</p>
          <div class="lb-nugget">The lesson under the morning: <b>a death costs one window, not the run.</b> The atomic floor.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="lb-thread" style="--node:var(--peg-Fs)">
          <div class="lb-th-h"><span class="lb-th-key">F# &middot; Fivier</span><h3 class="lb-th-name">The transcription tool, skilled</h3><span class="lb-th-rams">RAM 34&ndash;35</span></div>
          <p>The Meta Dates apparatus captured into the /fivier skill: the winning config, the atomic-resumable method, the audio-is-the-Source discipline.</p>
          <div class="lb-nugget">Olo found the tool hardcoded beam 1 and could not reproduce the winning config; the <b>--beam</b> fix closed a real reproducibility gap.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="lb-thread" style="--node:var(--peg-E)">
          <div class="lb-th-h"><span class="lb-th-key">E &middot; the OS</span><h3 class="lb-th-name">The operating model emerged, then met its correction</h3><span class="lb-th-rams">RAM 20,21,31&ndash;33</span></div>
          <p>Seven truths composed into one: NEST is Dan's AUTOSIM run outside his head. Two interpreters wrote it; Olo caught that the first draft had no Dan in it and restored the Director.</p>
